{"tid":2059110,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺小學教畜係仆街冚家鏟嚟","createTime":"2020-06-10T15:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T03:22:26.000Z","uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56f7f4ae4c2ec584dde18cb183e5b791471885d4","tid":2059110,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"雖然已經開左好多po 屌柒班撚樣<br />\n但我發覺小學真係太撚多教畜<br />\n所以會繼續開<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你老母 以前小3嗰陣有個咩中文書法比賽  要喺堂上做<br />\n咁我寫字唔靚係事實啦<br />\n但都無計照做<br />\n<br />\n隻英文教畜走埋嚟叫我幫手定做唔知乜 <br />\n咁我隔籬位話 我地有中文書法比賽wor<br />\n然後隻仆街教畜就話佢（我）都唔會贏架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係我屌你老母使唔撚使咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後某日老母就放學帶我飲茶啦<br />\n咁我食食下我同啲表親戚喺酒樓出面玩<br />\n又撞到嗰隻死教畜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又屌鳩我做咩放學唔翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你撚事咩閪婆！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌完隻閪婆屌另一隻教數學同VA嘅啊SIR<br />\n當時小學雞梗係有玩賽爾號嗰啲支那GAME<br />\n所以識簡體字<br />\n咁我就有時喺家課冊寫簡體字<br />\n然後俾個教畜屌鳩我咩享受香港福利 點解用簡體字<br />\n屌你老母 我知連登仔憎鳩殘體字 但佢洗唔洗喺到訓斥我啊屌你老母 搞到我以為同殘體字犯法<br />\n上到中學先知原來俾用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當時班上有個唔聽話嘅學生 坐唔定嗰隻<br />\n個教畜直頭係用麻繩綁住個學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然小學雞嗰陣嘅心態係食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後條教畜無教<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後又有一隻白髮魔女教畜<br />\n做得我啊婆<br />\n唔知邊個發明午膳唔俾離開個位呢個弱智規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同時發明膳長呢個崗位<br />\n無錯我就係膳長<br />\n咁派飯梗係要行嚟行去架啦閪婆！<br />\n咁佢巡到我班房就見到我唔喺位 就的我出去鬧<br />\n然後解釋我係膳長xyz 先放翻我<br />\n屌你老母屌你老母屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母真係要移民先好生仔女 香港教育完全無自由可言<br />\n屌你老母香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母死教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日搞鳩學生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187f77f2c8b662783948ace8c1f9e87138bb1056","tid":2059110,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"fa7ba173436ee3a4250494ba964e231e392e2e90","tid":2059110,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"yesss!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0116e631d8f349b3a28b71ae28b81990a9fc5c24","tid":2059110,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"香港地都唔知有冇兩成教師真係有使命有承擔想作育英才<br />\n大部份都係為份糧<br />\n而小學教師頂薪低過中學<br />\n有少少質素嘅都去教中學啦"},{"pid":"6ee67e768b10f4f975fd1bb89746532407f244c0","tid":2059110,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa7ba173436ee3a4250494ba964e231e392e2e90","tid":2059110,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"yesss!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186ce780adc1d5d035f31ed10761664b079f1783","tid":205911